Modulsicht:

1. Common
	- User
		- int Id
		- string Name
		- string Password
		- enum Role
		- int MatchCount
		- int WinCount
		- int Points
	- Question
		- int Id
		- string Text
		- string[] answers
		- enum category
	- Match
		- int Id?
		- User player1, player2
		- int points1, points2

2. Server
	- QuestionController
		- bool Add(question)
		- bool Remove(question)
		- bool Update(question)
		- List<Question> Get()
		- void Backup()
		- ? Export()
		- bool Import(?)
	- UserController
		- bool Add(user)
		- bool Remove(user)
		- bool Update(user)
		- List<User> Get()
		- User Login(name, password)
		- void Logout()
		- List<User> GetOnline()
		- List<User> GetRankedUsers(offset, length)
		- void Backup()
		- ? Export()
		- bool Import(?)
	- MatchController
		- bool RequestMatch(user)
		- bool ConnectPlayers(user1, user2) -> app.MatchFound
		- bool SendChallenge(from, to)      -> app.ChallengeReceived
		- bool AcceptChallenge(from, to)    -> app.ChallengeAccepted
		- bool RemoveChallenges(user)
		- bool SubmitAnswer(q_index)		 -> app.OpponentAnswered
		- List<Match> GetUserMatches(user)

3. Client
3.1 App
	3.1.1 to server
		- bool Register(name, password) -> UserController.Add
		- User Login(name, password)    -> UserController.Login
		- bool Logout()			  -> MatchController.RemoveChallenges / UserController.Logout
		- bool ChangeUserData(name, 
			   oldPw, newPw, newPw)    -> UserController.Update
		- bool DisplayRankings(offset, 
						   length)  -> UserController.GetRankedUsers
		- bool RequestMatch()		  -> MatchController.RequestMatch
		- void DisplayOnlineUsers()     -> UserController.GetOnline
		- bool Challenge(user)		  -> MatchController.SendChallenge
		- bool GameStart()			  -> MatchController.RemoveChallenges
		- bool SubmitAnswer(q_index)    -> MatchController.SubmitAnswer

	3.1.2 from server
		- void MatchFound(user)
		- void ChallengeReceived(user)
		- void ChallengeAccepted(user)
		- void OpponentAnswered(q_index)

	3.1.3 local
		- void EndMatch()
		- void PlayOffline()
		- void DisplayOwnStatistics()
		- void DisplaySettings()

3.2 HTML
	- "/login/"		  -> UserController.Login
	- "/questions/		  -> QuestionController.Get
	- "/questions/add"	  -> QuestionController.Add
	- "/questions/remove" -> QuestionController.Remove
	- "/questions/edit"	  -> QuestionController.Update
	- "/questions/export" -> QuestionController.Export
	- "/questions/import" -> QuestionController.Import
	- "/users/"		  -> UserController.Get
	- "/users/add"		  -> UserController.Add
	- "/users/remove"	  -> UserController.Remove
	- "/users/edit"	  -> UserController.Update
	- "/users/export"	  -> UserController.Export
	- "/users/import"	  -> UserController.Import

